      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about the money though. it's the fact that i'm some kind of joke now. everyone who believed in me is gonna see me as this pathetic guy who couldn't handle a downturn. i feel like there's no version of the future where i'm not just a walking embarrassment. it feels like the only way to make the shame stop is to just... not be here to feel it anymore.",
